title: Israel Launches Deadly Strikes on Gaza, Saying Militants Attacked Its Soldiers
summary_full: Gaza officials said the Israeli airstrikes killed at least 21 Palestinians. Israel said one of its soldiers was critically wounded in the attack by Palestinian gunmen.
